Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.45,0:00:24.96,Black Title,,0,0,0,,{TIME:20450,24960}{\fs150\pos(906,346)}Kaori
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.76,0:00:30.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:28760,30380}It's lovely...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.21,0:00:34.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:31210,34550}This... is for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.13,0:00:39.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:38130,39760}Kaori, are you ready yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:40920,42270}Sorry, I'll be right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.14,0:00:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:43140,44760}Kaori will be thrilled.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.76,0:00:46.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:44760,46760}I'm sure it will look good on her.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.76,0:00:50.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:46760,50050}Takayuki is my mother's{mama idk} younger brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.76,0:00:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:50760,53190}It came as a shock when he got married last year.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.20,0:00:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:54200,56040}It's made him much more gentle.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.48,0:01:00.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:56480,60450}I just know that Takayuki has to be my prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.45,0:01:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:60450,61720}That sounds serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.38,0:01:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:63380,64060}I'm ready.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.22,0:01:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:76220,77050}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.48,0:01:24.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:81480,84850}Women sure are scary, huh? I didn't know they could change this much.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.32,0:01:27.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:86320,87600}You're over exaggerating.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.60,0:01:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:87600,90320}No, I mean it. You look really cute.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.96,0:01:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:90960,91770}It really suits you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.16,0:01:34.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:93160,94690}Takayuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.70,0:01:47.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:103700,107940} If I wore that, I could dance with Takayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.49,0:02:12.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:131490,132940}Oh, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.42,0:02:14.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133420,134940}I must have fallen asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.41,0:02:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:135410,136650}There must have been a power cut.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.02,0:02:22.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:140020,142030}Oh, no. What have I...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.46,0:02:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142460,145930}I must have put this on last night when thinking of Takayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.44,0:02:28.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:147440,148960}That's ridiculous.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.37,0:02:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:150370,152420}What a relief that it didn't get creased.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.85,0:02:49.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:168850,169850}Was that me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.66,0:02:58.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:176660,178120}Or was it mama...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.74,0:03:03.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:179740,183040}That's right, it must be papa coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.14,0:03:12.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:187140,192240}{not too sure on this tbh}Darling, it's late, why are you going to that woman's place?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.24,0:03:14.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:192240,194460}{as above lol} Don't you care about Kaori?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.00,0:03:16.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:196000,196800}Darling...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.12,0:03:20.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199120,200170}Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.17,0:03:22.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201170,202170}Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.69,0:03:23.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:202690,203690}Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.26,0:03:25.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:205260,205890}Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.17,0:03:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207170,209200}Kaori, it's time to get up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.64,0:03:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:212640,213980}What are you doing, Kaori?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:43.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:219480,223650}I know you're happy, but it's childish to go to sleep in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.60,0:03:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:225600,226860}I was...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.86,0:03:47.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226860,227950}That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.96,0:03:51.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228960,231240}I changed! I really did!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.54,0:03:54.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231540,234810}What are you talking about?\N Hurry up and wash your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.46,0:03:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236460,238880}Mama, where's papa?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.78,0:04:02.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:239780,242650}He's working, like he usually is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:09.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245330,249120}I feel so sorry for her...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.08,0:04:16.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:252080,256220}Is there anything I can do about\N my mother's mental breakdown?{ ノイローゼ }
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:256220,257250}Mental breakdown?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.25,0:04:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257250,258480}Has something happened?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.80,0:04:23.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:258800,263450}It's just... what do I do about last night?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.52,0:04:28.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:264520,268930}When I woke up, I was wearing the one piece. I'm sure I took it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.93,0:04:30.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:268930,270180}One piece?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:33.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:270760,273500}You sure you weren't just tired?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.50,0:04:35.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:273500,275500}I wonder about that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.48,0:04:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:276480,277380}All rise!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.36,0:04:44.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:283360,284720}What's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.05,0:04:47.81,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285050,287810}Oh... it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.81,0:04:48.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:287810,288680}I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.58,0:04:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289580,293530}How... did it get like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.66,0:05:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:299660,302320}It's all because of {\i1}that{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.64,0:05:08.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:306640,308290}But, it's so pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.12,0:05:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313120,316720}Takayuki, please save me...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.60,0:05:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:326600,327660}Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.98,0:05:30.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328980,330040}Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.86,0:05:32.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:330860,332040}Kaori.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.21,0:05:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333210,334040}Kaori!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.16,0:05:39.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:336160,339480}You have to stop this, it's strange.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.45,0:05:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341450,342930}What is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.00,0:06:00.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356000,360340}Kaori! Kaori! Kaori, get a hold of yourself!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.54,0:06:16.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376540,376930}Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.54,0:06:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:379540,383740}I'm thankful that you came all this way, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.78,0:06:31.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388780,391600}It's better if you just look from here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.60,0:06:33.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391600,393660}If she notices you, she'll get excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.96,0:06:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:404960,408720}No matter how many times she changes, it's no good.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.56,0:06:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:409560,411180}It's that one piece.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.96,0:06:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:412960,414140}It keeps coming back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.80,0:06:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:414800,418980}{saishou no one piece wa toku ni aiteshimaimashita?}At the start I tried to take the one piece off.{pretty sure this is wrong}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.49,0:07:05.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:419490,425610}{otouto to futari de hagitotte, tokuni aiteshimattan desu kedo ne} Then my brother and I tried to do tear it, but it wouldn't come off.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.60,0:07:08.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426600,428330}It wouldn't work, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.78,0:07:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428780,433530}But the other day, after touching it, I finally understood.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:17.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:433530,437040}It's just her skin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.45,0:07:21.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:439450,441900}That's just what it has become.
